column5: I have a XXL Mustang Float suit that was warn 2-3 times then stored inside.  If it would fit you and you could pick it up in Mississauga or Orangeville I will let it go for a steal.  Thought I would put a line up here, I won't need it at all when I move.
Ahh yes, the size formerly known as FF.
I have an XL that someone can use. Still has no slime on it. In Fonthill..Gimme a shout.
Bitsmith got mine..hope like heck you don't need it.
